reference points, no meaningful motion, no time, no wave fronts...
then at a larger scale it becomes hyperspace and we get EM waves,
strings/branes and the quantum, and finally, at an even larger scale,
we get Einstein's spacetime, the objective universe as we naturally
perceive it.

1) The Aether - (Sub-quantum level), dimensionless, eternal. A
Hawking's singularity or Hiley's 'pre-space'. Previously considered as
an entity, a medium for fields to propagate through, by great minds
like Maxwell, Lorentz, Einstein... and more recently treted as the
